le for ensuring that all materials including letters of reference are submitted by the deadline please do not submit supplemental materials such as books lengthy manuscripts or more than the required number of recommendations please note that recommenders may upload their letters prior to the applicant's official submission of his her application it is much preferred that your recommenders upload their letters through the online system but if that is simply not possible recommenders may email their letters of recommendation to cisacfellowship stanford edu online submission of application will include completed online application form resume cv graduate school transcript unofficial transcripts are acceptable all pre and postdoctoral applicants must include a transcript junior faculty and professionals may include a transcript but are not required to do so research project prospectus or description of dissertation 1500 word max three confidential letters of recommendation and no more than three please to be submitted online directly by the recommender online application instructions 1 go to https www applyweb com apply cisac 2 click create your account input requested information to create username and password 3 click online cisac 2012 2013 fellowship application 4 proceed through three page application entering inputs in all required fields 5 electronically sign and submit application on bottom of page 3 6 print a copy or save an electronic pdf file of your application submission for your records contact info for more information about fellowships please contact cisac fellowship program freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall c206 7 616 serra st stanford university stanford ca 94305 6165 usa phone 650 725 9132 fax 650 723 0089 cisacfellowship stanford edu search cisac search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli instit